### Test các endpoint của PricingService thông qua API Gateway

### 1. GET - Lấy pricing cơ bản
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing

### 2. GET - Lấy pricing theo ID
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing/123

### 3. POST - Tính toán pricing
POST http://localhost:5050/pricing
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "basePrice": 1000,
  "quantity": 5,
  "taxRate": 0.1
}

### 4. PUT - Cập nhật pricing
PUT http://localhost:5050/pricing/123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPrice": 1500,
  "newPrice": 1800
}

### 5. DELETE - Xóa pricing
DELETE http://localhost:5050/pricing/123